---
title: Pork Gyro Inspired Dinner with Garlic Yogurt
description: Pulled pork gets the "gyro" treatment with Mediterranean spices and fresh oregano. Garlic-spiked yogurt and roasted taters fill out the rest of this tasty pita dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/porc-style-gyros-aa564e68.jpg
